    dc:description "Figure 3. Allodorylaimus kazirangus sp. nov. (A) Anterior region, (B) anterior end showing amphid, (C) pharyngeal expansion, (D) anterior genital branch, (E) vulval region, (F) female posterior region, (G) female posterior end, (G) male posterior region, (H) male posterior end." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5204927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5204929>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Allodorylaimus kazirangus sp. nov. (A–D) Anterior region, (E) pharyngo–intestinal junction, (F) vulval region, (G) female genital branch showing uterus, (H,I) female posterior end, (J) male posterior region. Scale bars: A–C,E,F,H,I = 10 µm; D,G,J = 20 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5204929/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

